findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInReward(), eligibleSupply() and eligibleSupplyAt(), unban() uses a loop to find and remove addresses from lists which can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if the list is too long.

findings.title: No Transfer event emitted on taking a fee
findings.description: The contract does not emit a Transfer event when taking a fee and the amount written in the event is incorrect.
